     D  Q2MORI       E                     EXTFLD(QQMORI)                                     CGL029
     D  Q2DOPI       E                     EXTFLD(QQDOPI)                                     CGL029
     D  Q2MOPI       E                     EXTFLD(QQMOPI)                                     CGL029
     D  Q2RONS       E                     EXTFLD(QQRONS)                                     CGL029
     D  Q2PONS       E                     EXTFLD(QQPONS)                                     CGL029
