      ** Index for arrays of of error message ids etc
     D Idx             S              3P 0

      ** Index for arrays of warning message ids etc
     D WIdx            S              3P 0

     D PSard           S              6A
     D CAS004          S              1A
     D CDL019          S              1A                                                      CDL019
     D CDL020          S              1A                                                      CDL020
     D @TimeStamp      S             26A                                                      CAP191
     D AAuth           S              1A                                                      CAP191
